@startuml 02_secuencia_credito
!theme plain
title Flujo de Solicitud de Credito - CMAC Maynas

actor "Cliente" as CLI
participant "Homebanking\n:8173" as HB
participant "Backend Node.js\n:3000" as API
participant "Supabase\nPostgreSQL" as DB
actor "Asesor" as ASE
actor "Comite" as COM

CLI -> HB: Inicia sesion
HB -> API: POST /api/auth/login
API -> DB: signInWithPassword
DB --> API: JWT token + usuario
API --> HB: token + usuario
HB --> CLI: Redirige a Dashboard

CLI -> HB: Nueva Solicitud de Credito
HB -> API: POST /api/credito/solicitar\n+ Bearer token
API -> API: Calcula cuota\n(TEA 40.92% o 43.92%)
API -> DB: INSERT solicitudes_prestamo
DB --> API: solicitud creada
API --> HB: cuota_mensual + estado
HB --> CLI: Solicitud enviada exitosamente

ASE -> API: GET /api/mora/\n+ Bearer token (rol: asesor)
API -> DB: SELECT mora_creditos
DB --> API: registros de mora
API --> ASE: bandas R1/R2/R3

ASE -> API: POST /api/mora/gestion
API -> DB: UPDATE estado_gestion
DB --> API: gestion registrada

COM -> API: POST /api/mora/judicial\n(rol: comite)
API -> DB: UPDATE banda = judicial
DB --> API: credito derivado

@enduml